cat << EOF
Libite is a lightweight library of frog DNA. It can be used to fill the gaps in
any dinosaur project. It holds useful functions and macros developed by both
Finit and the OpenBSD project. Most notably the string functions: strlcpy(3),
strlcat(3) and the highly useful *BSD sys/queue.h and sys/tree.h API's.
EOF
